    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行 9 月利率会议将“全面开放”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-s-september-rate-meeting-will-be-wide-open</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行下次利率会议将“完全开放”，但政策制定者将掌握更多信息来决定是否有必要再次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/lagarde-says-ecb-s-september-rate-meeting-will-be-wide-open</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其取悦投资者的货币政策在国内面临批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/turkey-s-investor-pleasing-currency-policy-faces-critics-at-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高利率和可预测的货币相结合，使土耳其成为外国投资者异常安全的选择，但随着出口商失去业务和经济放缓，对这种组合的批评也越来越多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/turkey-s-investor-pleasing-currency-policy-faces-critics-at-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，阿达尼和丰益集团将选择银行出售合资企业的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/adani-wilmar-are-said-to-pick-banks-for-sale-of-stake-in-jv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 和丰益国际有限公司 (Wilmar International Ltd.) 已选定银行协助出售其消费合资企业阿达尼丰益国际有限公司 (Adani Wilmar Ltd.) 的少数股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/adani-wilmar-are-said-to-pick-banks-for-sale-of-stake-in-jv</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国金币销量因对工党财政计划的担忧而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-gold-coin-sales-jump-on-concerns-over-labour-s-fiscal-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心新工党政府可能改变财政政策，英国皇家铸币厂有限公司的免税金币销量在上个季度出现增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-gold-coin-sales-jump-on-concerns-over-labour-s-fiscal-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 13:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
